    {
      "parameters": {
        "text": "Welcome to QuantumVector AI! 🤖\n\nI'm here to help you with:\n\n📚 *FAQs* - Get answers to common questions\n📅 *Book Services* - Schedule a consultation\n💬 *General Inquiries* - Learn about our AI solutions\n\nType /services to see what we offer, /pricing for pricing details, /contact for contact info, or /help to see all commands.",
