      "parameters": {
        "text": "Our AI Services:\n\n1️⃣ *Customer Care Chatbots* - $2,500/mo\n   24/7 AI-powered customer support\n\n2️⃣ *Marketing Content Generation* - $1,500/mo\n   SEO-optimized content at scale\n\n3️⃣ *Lead Generation & Qualification* - $3,000/mo\n   Automated lead scoring\n\n4️⃣ *Custom LLM Development* - From $25,000\n   Domain-specific language models\n\n5️⃣ *Predictive Analytics* - $4,000/mo\n   AI-powered forecasting\n\n6️⃣ *Document Intelligence* - $2,000/mo\n   OCR and data extraction\n\n7️⃣ *Voice AI Solutions* - $3,500/mo\n   Speech-to-text & voice assistants\n\n8️⃣ *Computer Vision* - $5,000/mo\n   Image recognition & QC\n\n9️⃣ *AI-Powered Search* - $2,500/mo\n   Semantic search solutions\n\n🔟 *AI Integration Consulting* - $10,000/project\n   Strategic AI guidance\n\n1️⃣1️⃣ *Customer Service Hub* - $6,000/mo\n   Omnichannel support platform\n\n\nType /book to book a service!",
