        "text": "💰 *Pricing Plans*\n\n*Starter* - Ksh 129,870/month\n• AI Chatbot Integration\n• Basic Data Analysis\n• 5 Custom Models\n• Email Support\n\n*Professional* - Ksh 389,870/month\n• Everything in Starter\n• Advanced Predictive Analytics\n• 20 Custom Models\n• Priority Support\n• Dedicated Account Manager\n\n*Enterprise* - Custom Pricing\n• Unlimited Custom Models\n• 24/7 Premium Support\n• On-Premise Deployment\n• SLA Guarantee\n\nAll prices include 16% VAT.\nType /book to get started!",
